<li><span style="page:WordSection9"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino"><span style="color:black">Unknown, possibly chronic overproduction of pro-inflammatory cytokines such as <b>VEGF</b></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
